{"tid":1403420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉載自高登】 (有圖)中國國安出動混入示威者之中","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:10:57.000Z","uid":17031,"like":572,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fd7dc73b781b03a1031071f2e0a48d7bdfdbb7","tid":1403420,"uid":17031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7093757%2Fpage%2F1&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7fea85c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong>(有圖)中國國安出動混入示威者之中,中共明顥不再信任香港警察</strong><br />\n昨晚10點左右，我夢見自己正在馬鞍山警察局對出，我地義士發現一名可疑的攝影師向人群影大頭同錄影。<br />\n佢著住件背後印有日文字的記者背心。我地質問他!他不停講&ldquo;sumimasan&rdquo;，假扮係一個真正的日本記者和掉左自己部電話。我地執左佢部電話發現係用簡體,同所有信息/大頭相已經用微信發送。<br />\n<br />\n但義士最後放左佢走，我同另一人吊住佢尾,他行前500米坐底左。佢用普通話打電話俾其他人,我地問佢點解頭先講日文唔用普通話回答我們,當我地質問時，他聲稱自己患有高血壓，並且希望我地幫佢打電話CALL白車或<br />\n送他去醫院（用普通話說出）。我地叫佢自己打,繼續問他的背景細節，他為誰工作等等。<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後，有一名可疑既香港人帶左兩個救護員過黎,。我們看到救護員遞左張紙俾佢,同時可疑既香港人無啦啦試圖解釋點解會帶醫務人員過黎！<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣大批軍裝到場驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n義士們要小心內地人樣既記者，因為佢地都係假扮！我從一些國內商家得知中國共產黨已派遣相當數量既人（4000至5000人）偽裝成義士或記者想從我地當中獲取更多資訊同義士大頭相。<br />\n<br />\n我發現當我們識別佢地身份既時候會好害怕，因為佢地可能已經違反法律，當然警察唔會對佢地採取任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔應該咁輕易放佢地走!我地要出手令佢地講出身份/目的!起碼要了解到中央既目的同手段！知己知彼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/y8LXOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fy8LXOM.png&h=d7969a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/hCYbcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FhCYbcn.png&h=5893ae88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pmHLB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FpmHLB2.png&h=ee788bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/FjIYn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FFjIYn7.png&h=1150ba1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/VuIkA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FVuIkA4.png&h=641a76d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pu2s6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fpu2s6S.png&h=d017f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/ktj3o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fktj3o4.png&h=4064c1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/IEJHTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FIEJHTP.png&h=6c3a449f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b48c339a40b1251c8ee091cf390162e2c239532","tid":1403420,"uid":248470,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"非《一次又一次難清場》<br />\n是《一次又一次難拉人》"},{"pid":"d4481d13bf2e09ccae7bce349aff0c1310bcdc61","tid":1403420,"uid":17031,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>任務失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f94a329105470ef8ecf44f4b5b32b8c84c68c6fd","tid":1403420,"uid":52364,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:56:41.000Z","msg":"巴打做咩唔戴手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9701e9ce796d56b7541cea27557a69bac3ec532","tid":1403420,"uid":166942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47a24a9b7abda9f9fdf2dcf59e98863ad502d8e","tid":1403420,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4193dd631598742b188f9084d7d8b80e7a2e6d73","tid":1403420,"uid":207470,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"之前都喺荔枝角同其他地方見過全黑打扮<br />\n但講普通話嘅人<br />\n要提防"},{"pid":"5eed64872adec505033329b02e21854ffd5fa26d","tid":1403420,"uid":68493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a5e51732b0cb892b6288f50e3e686d3efcf64c3d","tid":1403420,"uid":208722,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"推，極嚴重"},{"pid":"5801c8cad6b6e62afe4467eeaf5daeda44ad7662","tid":1403420,"uid":265256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"99e2786d0971332a3cb0369cf1843619b79299bb","tid":1403420,"uid":259613,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"點解唔打"},{"pid":"927fcc6bf38d5babfb64fbef9f51507ef944902b","tid":1403420,"uid":28223,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:01:09.000Z","msg":"係個群打曬咁多年中共最唔想聽到既野先比返佢呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87c1f2b169ba813854dcd05f0eb09a8351b85b7","tid":1403420,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c346353b102d3643034b5753616058de3693f3f","tid":1403420,"uid":189109,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"建東個WECHAT ID你唔撚影......"},{"pid":"5906fb175c11379ce4ba0b8748f248564350be11","tid":1403420,"uid":112748,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"d0fd7dc73b781b03a1031071f2e0a48d7bdfdbb7","tid"