/>\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/VuIkA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FVuIkA4.png&h=641a76d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pu2s6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fpu2s6S.png&h=d017f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/ktj3o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fktj3o4.png&h=4064c1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/IEJHTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FIEJHTP.png&h=6c3a449f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"猛料黎喎，高登仔係事主？比左料蘋果未？依家佢處境好唔安全咁喎"},{"pid":"6a8c9f72cc7600e761174abf6fd52b37823d28b6","tid":1403420,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:12:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"144d0e0c3609dcdc8df03b84f6916b2b00ce158b","tid":1403420,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:18:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccd85327f02c86612a6df471b8a4d251ebfc5431","tid":1403420,"uid":285826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d0fd7dc73b781b03a1031071f2e0a48d7bdfdbb7","tid":1403420,"uid":17031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7093757%2Fpage%2F1&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7fea85c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong>(有圖)中國國安出動混入示威者之中,中共明顥不再信任香港警察</strong><br />\n昨晚10點左右，我夢見自己正在馬鞍山警察局對出，我地義士發現一名可疑的攝影師向人群影大頭同錄影。<br />\n佢著住件背後印有日文字的記者背心。我地質問他!他不停講&ldquo;sumimasan&rdquo;，假扮係一個真正的日本記者和掉左自己部電話。我地執左佢部電話發現係用簡體,同所有信息/大頭相已經用微信發送。<br />\n<br />\n但義士最後放左佢走，我同另一人吊住佢尾,他行前500米坐底左。佢用普通話打電話俾其他人,我地問佢點解頭先講日文唔用普通話回答我們,當我地質問時，他聲稱自己患有高血壓，並且希望我地幫佢打電話CALL白車或<br />\n送他去醫院（用普通話說出）。我地叫佢自己打,繼續問他的背景細節，他為誰工作等等。<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後，有一名可疑既香港人帶左兩個救護員過黎,。我們看到救護員遞左張紙俾佢,同時可疑既香港人無啦啦試圖解釋點解會帶醫務人員過黎！<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣大批軍裝到場驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n義士們要小心內地人樣既記者，因為佢地都係假扮！我從一些國內商家得知中國共產黨已派遣相當數量既人（4000至5000人）偽裝成義士或記者想從我地當中獲取更多資訊同義士大頭相。<br />\n<br />\n我發現當我們識別佢地身份既時候會好害怕，因為佢地可能已經違反法律，當然警察唔會對佢地採取任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔應該咁輕易放佢地走!我地要出手令佢地講出身份/目的!起碼要了解到中央既目的同手段！知己知彼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/y8LXOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fy8LXOM.png&h=d7969a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/hCYbcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FhCYbcn.png&h=5893ae88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pmHLB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FpmHLB2.png&h=ee788bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/FjIYn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FFjIYn7.png&h=1150ba1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/VuIkA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FVuIkA4.png&h=641a76d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pu2s6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fpu2s6S.png&h=d017f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/ktj3o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fktj3o4.png&h=4064c1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/IEJHTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FIEJHTP.png&h=6c3a449f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:11.000Z","msg":"其實我之前都收到台灣軍人朋友消息，話有情報話中國會有駐軍混入遊行，我仲以為係假&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"62957e0e858246e5046ee9592e053d0b0c6ec82b","tid":1403420,"uid":113183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:30:30.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"f67c59d08f2c2f9057733597466b66edf4426ad1","tid":1403420,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:31:31.000Z","msg":"共產黨一貫技倆<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">毫無人格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"623ad03c0df799e68527a679ccfb0763d41560d5","tid":1403420,"uid":50376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:33:38.000Z","msg":"推推佢<br />\n喱單料要跟"},{"pid":"69b9acf9dbb987a3e7fa1154c0664816e52fa6a8","tid":1403420,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"凡講支語一律視作鬼"},{"pid":"70988578cf6800f32d74319a7aa9c5cf814f9e85","tid":1403420,"uid":34448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:37:30.000Z","msg":"死大陸閪"},{"pid":"7b48a445dbc73f8eef0d8545128c471e77a39593","tid":1403420,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:40:44.000Z","msg":"應該要捉去一個地方問多啲料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cbfa2f73a0fe5f2ead2cd4b68543bafc8f2da3","tid":1403420,"uid":140411,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"cit