11.000Z","msg":"國安講日文係咩玩法"},{"pid":"24c842cef80445390e045ab180d69124969705aa","tid":1403420,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53c7fab44e74da1331f2b80e12de6db85b2c23e0","tid":1403420,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:47:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d3568a324d69bfeab773787ce44998f1797c8a6c","tid":1403420,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:48:12.000Z","msg":"所以戀戰、引戰、甚至盛傳對狗做既計劃，同埋獲取情報"},{"pid":"ccc6fa489f485d3ea17c4d439b091e44fcb47c52","tid":1403420,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:48:16.000Z","msg":"你们腥港人太善良了..."},{"pid":"0d72843b0aca94b5deb90e4fb98639b16bbf1329","tid":1403420,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:48:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa6f51da1ec91651322835d30cff4aad5c9d0001","tid":1403420,"uid":217080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2148b7ff8b16b5ced382858ba1c28d44f9bd90e6","tid":1403420,"uid":295572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0fd7dc73b781b03a1031071f2e0a48d7bdfdbb7","tid":1403420,"uid":17031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7093757%2Fpage%2F1&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7fea85c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7093757/page/1</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong>(有圖)中國國安出動混入示威者之中,中共明顥不再信任香港警察</strong><br />\n昨晚10點左右，我夢見自己正在馬鞍山警察局對出，我地義士發現一名可疑的攝影師向人群影大頭同錄影。<br />\n佢著住件背後印有日文字的記者背心。我地質問他!他不停講&ldquo;sumimasan&rdquo;，假扮係一個真正的日本記者和掉左自己部電話。我地執左佢部電話發現係用簡體,同所有信息/大頭相已經用微信發送。<br />\n<br />\n但義士最後放左佢走，我同另一人吊住佢尾,他行前500米坐底左。佢用普通話打電話俾其他人,我地問佢點解頭先講日文唔用普通話回答我們,當我地質問時，他聲稱自己患有高血壓，並且希望我地幫佢打電話CALL白車或<br />\n送他去醫院（用普通話說出）。我地叫佢自己打,繼續問他的背景細節，他為誰工作等等。<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後，有一名可疑既香港人帶左兩個救護員過黎,。我們看到救護員遞左張紙俾佢,同時可疑既香港人無啦啦試圖解釋點解會帶醫務人員過黎！<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣大批軍裝到場驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n義士們要小心內地人樣既記者，因為佢地都係假扮！我從一些國內商家得知中國共產黨已派遣相當數量既人（4000至5000人）偽裝成義士或記者想從我地當中獲取更多資訊同義士大頭相。<br />\n<br />\n我發現當我們識別佢地身份既時候會好害怕，因為佢地可能已經違反法律，當然警察唔會對佢地採取任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔應該咁輕易放佢地走!我地要出手令佢地講出身份/目的!起碼要了解到中央既目的同手段！知己知彼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/y8LXOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fy8LXOM.png&h=d7969a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/hCYbcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FhCYbcn.png&h=5893ae88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pmHLB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FpmHLB2.png&h=ee788bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/FjIYn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FFjIYn7.png&h=1150ba1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/VuIkA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FVuIkA4.png&h=641a76d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/pu2s6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fpu2s6S.png&h=d017f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/ktj3o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fktj3o4.png&h=4064c1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/IEJHTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FIEJHTP.png&h=6c3a449f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:51:21.000Z","msg":"推。check手機d料，所有contact share 曬出黎"},{"pid":"7c30bd0a455884b470820b5dd6d5370e4555590b","tid":1403420,"uid":232863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:52:33.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">重要野,要推。8月5齊罷工。永不離棄義士\n試著說 Hit and run。不要說 Be water\n------------------\n光復香港,時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bdbfc9202f3e5bdbae81f92af610b015fa50a012","tid":1403420,"uid":177270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:54:27.000Z","msg":"一定要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2275a72448d8ed7ff33ffd0b66b87df78031195","tid":1403420,"uid":5623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:08.000Z","msg":"想問係點知真係國安？<br />\n因為就咁睇圖只係睇到係一個大陸閪"},{"pid":"0407f67a44c8794e000a92a69ae7fcdcbbf24f19","tid":1403420,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:04:55.000Z","msg":"去得勞改啦"},{"pid":"7ba4c66c948af2306d17619117e61db098288238","tid":1403420,"uid":75026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"512b3ceddd6755d1b51e27aafdb0f06022791163","tid":1403420,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da65efc10e12ee7f94f1b8839897ffbd02f0231","tid":1403420,"uid":40790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a482e0db4c2deccbe5c97d3437aa2558a6dfa3","tid":1403420,"uid":5549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:13:05.000Z","msg":"一早講左一定會有鬼混入前線，呢招係共產黨既看家本領，係你地班on9死都話唔好捉鬼唔好割席，前線做乜on9野都要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"